Autumn has just come and you have received a letter from the popular and most gorgeous Queen Elsa. You are her first choice to meet during this season. Lots of preparations to do before her coming for you! No need to get confused as you can complete the goal of the game successfully by just paying attention to the details. Are you ready to accept this challenge? Join Hello Autumn Hello Elsa game and be ready to make all the arrangements before the important meeting!
Firstly, you have to pick up the correct fruits on the tree and then dress up your girl in this brand new dressing game for girls. Choose some bananas, apples, guavas and other fruits from multiple trees! Autumn will become fabulous when the delicious fruits are served on the table. Guide Elsa to collect the scrumptious autumn fruits like apple, oranges, grapes and more! Prepare a letter showing your love to Elsa! Hurry up, friends! Click the next button and get ready to have a blast in this one of the best html5 girls games that are playable on multiple devices, no download required on atmegame.com!
